title: Does this video show six Antiva members beating someone up during a meeting in August 2018?
subtitle: An old video showing a group of fascists beating right-wing activists in Berkeley, California, was exchanged as if it had shown a recent incident in Washington, D.C.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: A video showing six members of Antefa beat up a person during an oath protest in August 2018 in Washington, D.C.
